{"tid":1222403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈譴責黑警打到示威者就盲","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:10:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T01:43:55.000Z","uid":85242,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de8e4be3766ef9129638b374d6af7ec116630738","tid":1222403,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:10:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/339997/逃犯條例-示威者被橡膠子彈擊中險盲-非致命武器-殺傷力強\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F339997%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%A9%A1%E8%86%A0%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E6%93%8A%E4%B8%AD%E9%9A%AA%E7%9B%B2-%E9%9D%9E%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8-%E6%AE%BA%E5%82%B7%E5%8A%9B%E5%BC%B7&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=e355a530\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/339997/逃犯條例-示威者被橡膠子彈擊中險盲-非致命武器-殺傷力強</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28mLDhh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28mLDhh.png&h=26aadb3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有網民昨日晚上在FACEBOOK上載數張相片，指是朋友於示威現場被橡膠子彈擊中</span>，並留言：「畀大家睇下朋友被橡膠彈擦面而過，都傷成咁樣！」相片可見傷者的左邊面受傷，留下一道傷口及流血，傷痕很深。<br />\n<br />\n上載相片的網民向《香港01》記者表示，受傷的朋友在立法會衝突中被警方的橡膠子彈射中臉頰，留下一道3厘米傷口，差5厘米便會射中左眼，險盲。她引述傷者說，中彈一刻感到很痛，現仍在港島區一間醫院留醫，<span style=\"color: red;\">但她不便透露更多細節。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男教師傷個眼角 幾偏新聞係現場採訪，呢個傷撚到盲咁濟無記者採訪，無義士拍片作實？ 記者做唔到野 炒撚左去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n義士點對得住呢位受傷既勇者呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb35d5f1ad519ae3ae6f7f9844078f93c68aa7a","tid":1222403,"uid":56505,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:21:10.000Z","msg":"樓主危險 快走"},{"pid":"e